      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Hardware\" title=\"Hardware\">Hardware</a> * Macintosh</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Macintosh_128k_transparency.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Macintosh_128k_transparency.png/330px-Macintosh_128k_transparency.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"352\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Macintosh_128k_transparency.png/500px-Macintosh_128k_transparency.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e3/Macintosh_128k_transparency.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Macintosh_128k_transparency.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Original Macintosh <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Macintosh</b>,<br />\na series of personal computers (PCs) designed, developed, and marketed by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Apple&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Apple (page does not exist)\">Apple Inc</a>, introduced on January 24, 1984 by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Jobs\">Steve Jobs</a>. It was the first mass-market personal computer featuring a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graphical_user_interface\">graphical user interface</a> and a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mouse_%28computing%29\">mouse</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Timeline\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Timeline</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#GUIs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">GUIs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Timeline\">Timeline</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Timeline\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> Model\n</th>\n<th> Year\n</th>\n<th> Processor\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macintosh_128K\">Macintosh 128K</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1984\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/68000\" title=\"68000\">68000</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macintosh_II\">Macintosh II</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1987\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/68020\" title=\"68020\">68020</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macintosh_IIx\">Macintosh IIx</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1988\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/68030\" title=\"68030\">68030</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macintosh_Quadra\">Macintosh Quadra</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1991\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/index.php?title=68040&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"68040 (page does not exist)\">68040</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Power_Macintosh\">Power Mac</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1994\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/PowerPC\" title=\"PowerPC\">PowerPC</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IMac_G3\">iMac G3</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1998\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/PowerPC\" title=\"PowerPC\">PowerPC</a> G3\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IMac_G4\">iMac G4</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2002\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/PowerPC\" title=\"PowerPC\">PowerPC</a> G4\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IMac_G5\">iMac G5</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2004\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/PowerPC\" title=\"PowerPC\">PowerPC</a> G5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IMac_%28Intel-based%29\">iMac</a> (<a href=\"/Intel\" title=\"Intel\">Intel</a>)\n</td>\n<td>  2006\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/X86-64\" title=\"X86-64\">x86-64</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mac_Pro\">Mac Pro</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2006, 2013\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/X86-64\" title=\"X86-64\">x86-64</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MacBook_Air\">MacBook Air</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mac_Mini\">Mac Mini</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2020\n</td>\n<td>  <a href=\"/index.php?title=Apple_M1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Apple M1 (page does not exist)\">Apple M1</a>\n</td></tr></table>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"GUIs\">GUIs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: GUIs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Banksia_GUI\" title=\"Banksia GUI\">Banksia GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessX\" title=\"ChessX\">ChessX</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Cute_Chess\" title=\"Cute Chess\">Cute Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/HIARCS_Chess_Explorer\" title=\"HIARCS Chess Explorer\">HIARCS Chess Explorer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Scid_vs._PC\" title=\"Scid vs. PC\">Scid vs. PC</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Sigma&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Sigma (page does not exist)\">Sigma</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/XBoard\" title=\"XBoard\">XBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">Chess GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:Mac\" title=\"Category:Mac\">Macintosh Engines</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=IOS&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"IOS (page does not exist)\">iOS</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kathe_Spracklen#LadySargon\" title=\"Kathe Spracklen\">Kathe Spracklen - Lady Sargon</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ward_Douglas_Maurer\" title=\"Ward Douglas Maurer\">Ward Douglas Maurer</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.worldcat.org/title/assembly-language-programming-on-the-mac-with-mpw-second-draft/oclc/22190641\">Assembly language programming on the Mac with MPW</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Washington_University_School_of_Engineering_and_Applied_Science\">School of Engineering and Applied Science</a>,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Washington_University\">George Washington University</a>, GWU-IIST-90-20.&#160;» <a href=\"/Assembly\" title=\"Assembly\">Assembly</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/gnu.chess/browse_frm/thread/185bde65b524170d\">Re: Gnu Chess for the Mac</a> by <a href=\"/Urban_Koistinen\" title=\"Urban Koistinen\">Urban Koistinen</a>, <a href=\"/GNU_Chess#NewsGroup\" title=\"GNU Chess\">gnu.chess</a>, April 16, 1993&#160;» <a href=\"/GNU_Chess\" title=\"GNU Chess\">GNU Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/g/rec.games.chess.computer/c/tBLgKkNG5sg/m/4b0mL-o6lv0J\">Re: Macintosh Chess Software links page</a> by <a href=\"/William_Bryant\" title=\"William Bryant\">William Bryant</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, June 12, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=12843\">HIARCS 11.1 SP / MP Macintosh has arrived!</a> by rafowell, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Apr 03, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/HIARCS\" title=\"HIARCS\">HIARCS</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=17984\">Macintosh Glaurung users: Please help</a> by <a href=\"/Tord_Romstad\" title=\"Tord Romstad\">Tord Romstad</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 23, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Glaurung\" title=\"Glaurung\">Glaurung</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Macintosh&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42154\">good macintosh guy for UCI engine development</a> by <a href=\"/Sam_Hamilton\" title=\"Sam Hamilton\">Sam Hamilton</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 25, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.foro.meca-web.es/viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=72&amp;start=10#p1706\">Re: La Máquina Preservadora. Programas de Ajedrez</a> by Luis a, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Meca Foro</a>, May 30, 2013 (Spanish)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50992\">Stockfish Mac app</a> by <a href=\"/Daylen_Yang\" title=\"Daylen Yang\">Daylen Yang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53733\">computerchess on apple</a> by <a href=\"/Thorsten_Czub\" title=\"Thorsten Czub\">Thorsten Czub</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 17, 2014 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59544\">Distributing engines for Mac/OSX</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a> <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 17, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection